, you have an expert pal in the process. Reap the rewards without being wracked with uncertainty.<\/p>\n<p>Let\u2019s chat! <a href=\"https:\/\/app.borderbuddy.com\/calculator2\/public\/import\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Get a free quote<\/a> today and let BorderBuddy set you up for success.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Are you having trouble keeping your import\/export papers in order? BorderBuddy ensures you have the right documents for clearing your items seamlessly through customs. What is a commercial invoice? Every international shipment must have its own accompanying commercial invoice. A commercial invoice is an essential document required for international shipping. Its purpose is to provide&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":13,"featured_media":2707,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"inline_featured_image":false,"_genesis_hide_title":false,"_genesis_hide_breadcrumbs":false,"_genesis_hide_singular_image":false,"_genesis_hide_footer_widgets":false,"_genesis_custom_body_class":"","_genesis_custom_post_class":"","_genesis_layout":"","footnotes":""},"categories":[9],"tags":[],"acf":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v22.4 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>Commercial Invoices 101: When do I need one and how do I fill it out? &#187; Blog &#187; BorderBuddy<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"Are you having trouble keeping your import\/export papers in order? BorderBuddy ensures you have the right documents for clearing your items seamlessly\" \/>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/borderbuddy.com\/blog\/commercial-invoices-101-when-do-i-need-one-and-how-do-i-fill-it-out\/\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"en_US\" \/>\n<meta pr